	  			<tr>
	  				<td class="title">Parameters</td>
	  				<td class="content">
	  					Parameters marked with * are "required".
		  				<ul>
		  					<li>
		  						<span class="title">*listTabData (ArrayList of JQueryTabData)</span> : A list of JQueryTabData (object containing the title of the tab and the name of the block that has the content).
							</li>
		  					<li>
		  						<span class="title">activePanelId (int)</span> : The number of the tab to activate when the page is displayed on the client. 
							</li>
		  					<li>
		  						<span class="title">params (JSONObject)</span> : The slider parameters (please refer to jquery-ui documentation) 
							</li>
		  				</ul>
		  			</td>
	  			</tr>
	  	</table>
	  	
